      "rubric": "Judge the plan or delivery against the actual Janus chat workflow, not isolated widgets. A pass requires explicit coverage for: project/thread selection, new session launch, first user turn visibility, running and completed states, follow-up recovery, terminal drawer, browser/workbench routing, context/output/diff/review/info surfaces, keyboard/focus, empty and error states, no stale workspace metadata, no dead placeholder controls, and no layout overlap at narrow, medium, and wide widths. Blocking issues must identify the missing workflow step or evidence.\n",
      "type": "judge"
    },
